"title": "3272: Holy Spirit, in OT",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "3272: holy spirit, in ot",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The OT portrays the Holy Spirit as being active in creation, in equipping individuals for skilled tasks and in inspiring prophecy and revelation.</p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit as the presence of God</h2>\n<h3>He is active in creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:2\">GEN 1:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:4\">JOB 33:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:30\">PSA 104:30</a></p>\n<h3>He is present everywhere</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:7\">PSA 139:7</a></strong></p>\n<h3>His sovereignty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa34:16\">ISA 34:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:14\">EZK 37:14</a></p>\n<h3>All life is dependent on the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:14-Job34:15\">JOB 34:14–34:15</a></strong> <em>NIV footnote at verse 14.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:3\">GEN 6:3</a></p>\n<h3>He is present with God's people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:11-Isa63:14\">ISA 63:11–63:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:20\">NEH 9:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag2:5\">HAG 2:5</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit equips individuals</h2>\n<h3>For leadership</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:10\">JDG 3:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:17\">NUM 11:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num11:25-Num11:29\">NUM 11:25–11:29</a> <em>The gift of prophecy was given temporarily to the elders in order to establish them as leaders of God's people</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num27:18\">NUM 27:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:9\">DEU 34:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:34\">JDG 6:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:29\">JDG 11:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:25\">JDG 13:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:6\">1SA 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:6\">1SA 11:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:13\">1SA 16:13</a></p>\n<h3>In bringing revelation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:38-Gen41:39\">GEN 41:38–41:39</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:8-Dan4:9\">DAN 4:8–4:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:18\">DAN 4:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:11\">DAN 5:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:14\">DAN 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>By empowering the prophet</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek2:2\">EZK 2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:12\">EZK 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:14\">EZK 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:24\">EZK 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:3\">EZK 8:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:24\">EZK 11:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek43:5\">EZK 43:5</a></p>\n<h3>By giving special strength</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:6\">JDG 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:19\">JDG 14:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:14\">JDG 15:14</a></p>\n<h3>By guidance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:10\">PSA 143:10</a></p>\n<h3>In planning</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:12\">1CH 28:12</a></p>\n<h3>In craftsmanship</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:3-Exod31:5\">EXO 31:3–31:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod35:31-Exod35:35\">EXO 35:31–35:35</a></p>\n<h3>In building</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:6\">ZEC 4:6</a></p>\n<h2>The Holy Spirit inspires</h2>\n<h3>Prophecy</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:20\">2CH 24:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num24:2\">NUM 24:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:6\">1SA 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:10\">1SA 10:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:20\">1SA 19:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam19:23\">1SA 19:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:1\">2CH 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:14\">2CH 20:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa48:16\">ISA 48:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek11:5\">EZK 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic3:8\">MIC 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:21\">2PE 1:21</a></p>\n<h3>Teaching</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:20\">NEH 9:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a></p>\n<h3>Praise</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam23:1-2Sam23:2\">2SA 23:1–23:2</a></p>\n<h3>A declaration of allegiance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:18\">1CH 12:18</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of the awareness of the Holy Spirit's activity</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:12\">1KI 18:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs2:16\">2KI 2:16</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of grieving the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:10\">ISA 63:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:3\">GEN 6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:14\">1SA 16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:11\">PSA 51:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:33-Ps106:48\">PSA 106:33–106:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:1\">ISA 30:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic2:7\">MIC 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech7:12\">ZEC 7:12</a></p>\n<h2>Promises of the Holy Spirit for the future</h2>\n<h3>The Spirit and the Messiah</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:2\">ISA 11:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:1\">ISA 42:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1\">ISA 61:1</a></p>\n<h3>The outpouring of the Spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:28-Joel2:29\">JOL 2:28–2:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa32:15\">ISA 32:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:3\">ISA 44:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa59:21\">ISA 59:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:27\">EZK 36:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:14\">EZK 37:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek39:29\">EZK 39:29</a></p>",
